description:
Mô Tả Công Việc


              We are a young, ambitious, multinational financial firm and we are growing FAST. We are operating in the global financial blockchain industry where we offer our clients the access to all the available financial products in the worldwide market. Our team members are professional individuals across 3 continents (America, Europe & Asia) and we share a no-boundaries working environment. Let your customer service skills flourish with us when you join one of the most progressive companies out there.


              Responsibilities:

              •	Dealing directly with clients either electronically or by telephone;

              •	Respond promptly to clients’ inquiries;

              •	Identify and escalate priority issues;

              •	Direct request and unresolved issues to the designated departments;

              •	Record and maintain logs.


              Xem toàn bộ Mô Tả Công Việc

requirement:
Yêu Cầu Công Việc


              Competencies:

              •	Interpersonal skills;

              •	Communication skills – verbal and written;

              •	Problem analysis and problem solving;

              •	Attention to detail and accuracy;

              •	Customer support oriented.


              Requirements:

              •	Candidate must possess at least a Diploma in any field;

              •	Required language – Must be able to communicate in English and Vietnamese;

              •	Experience in servicing Financial institution’s customers is an advantage eg. Banking;

              •	Willing to work on shift hours;

              •	Fresh graduates are encouraged to apply.


              *Due to the large number of applicants, please kindly understand that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.


              Xem toàn bộ Yêu Cầu Công Việc
